burn(uint256).details: Destroys `tokenId`, but only the owner of this contract is able to do it. This function calls the internal function _burn from ERC721Identifier.sol

mint(string,string,string,address).details: Mints `tokenId` and transfers it to `to`, but only the owner of this contract is able to do it. This function calls the internal function _mint from ERC721Identifier.sol

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.
